-- Red Moon - Immune to shadow damage, radiates 300 shadow damage in 5 yds radius (should place red visual on player, 10 min, physical debuff)

-- Blood Boil - Deals 1800 fire damage to all players in 100 

-- Flock of Ravens - Spawns 12 Blood Ravens (display id 20496) next to random players in 100 yds radius. 

